ion Invariance for GR. We also\ndraw some motivation from M-Theory's use of Nambu Mathematics along the lines\nof Bagger, Lambert and Gustavsson, finding some qualitative distinctions\nbetween this, GR and Supergravity as regards how Background Independence is\nrealized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Aug 2019 16:58:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-09"}
