the transition from free-fermion behavior at short distances to unparticle\nphysics at intermediate distances to the physics of massive particles at long\ndistances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Aug 2019 22:17:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Aug 2019 13:03:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2020 13:28:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-16"}
