se results emphasize the strong dependence of the electronic properties of\nair-exposed GaN surfaces on adsorbates. As a result, we advocate the use of the\ncommon cleaning steps analyzed here to re-initialize at will GaN$(1\\bar{1}00)$\nand $(0001)$ surfaces into pre-defined states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 09:06:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
